metadata.name: The Snowy Day
metadata.description:
A girl went outside on a very snowy winter day. It snowed heavily, and the girl was a bit anxious because of the cold weather, yet, she was also amazed by the snowy scenery. 
Meanwhile, Snowflakes fell on the girl's long eyelashes.
This illustration was done when I went out on a snowy winter day, inspired by its color and scenery. 
(a large size of the illustration in jpeg or png format will be given to the collectors)
